description: Qiiwi Games AB operates as an interactive Swedish multi-platform social games developer. The company is headquartered in Alingsas, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2017-10-13. The firm focuses on developing mobile games aimed at Casual Gamers in the genres Trivia, Match-3, Word / Puzzle and Arcade. The firm's activities are divided into two business areas: Mobile games and E-learning products.
name: Qiiwi Games AB (publ)
